name: Larimer Health Dept.
tweet: Kids aged 5 to 11 are expected to be eligible for the Pfizer COVID vaccine soon. Talk with your child’s health care provider about any questions you may have as you consider vaccination for your child. You can also find answers at @CDCgov.
